# PHI-at-rest envelope encryption. MUST equal the .NET Encryption:Passphrase so
# both services share one platform.encryption_keys key per tenant (interop + unified
# DPDP key destruction). The AI service NEVER provisions keys; it fails closed if no
# active 'medical_history' key exists for the tenant.
# AI_ENCRYPTION_PASSPHRASE=dev-only-encryption-passphrase-replace-in-production
